sentence: Really it is a fine painting app , especially for the price ( free ) .
content: Really it is a fine painting app, especially for the price (free). I have no problem with it. There are no ads that I have dealt with and the colors are fine. However I have been looking for an app like the paint app on Microsoft computers, so I could copy images and paste them here or draw straight lines, and this app does not have these features.

sentence: This is a great app .
content: This is a great app. This is basically Photoshop. Now, you may be asking, why am I saying that this is Photoshop? The ability to load photos, layers, a transparent color, the stamp feature, and more, makes this the perfect substitute for Photoshop. I have edited many photos with this. Sure, it may have it's limitations, but it's still great.

sentence: So nearly a great app .
content: So nearly a great app. But saving works badly (you aren't prompted to choose a path), and the function i most need (pixel perfect crop) is impossible to use. It zones out every time you select it... and it's impossibly touchy and keeps committing before you've finished adjusting. I tried about 15 times or more before giving up. Real shame as this is almost, otherwise what all the other apps fall to be. (Simple and powerful)
replyContent: Fixing these issues is planned for the future. Sorry, we are just pro-bono volunteers working in our free time on this free open source non-profit project... any help, e.g., as a developer would be highly appreciated. Thanks!

sentence: The only app I 've actually sought actively to positively review .

So I use a lot of art software on my phone, a ridiculous amount, but this is still my standby and tbh fave. sentence: The best simple paint\drawing app I 've found .
content: The best simple paint\drawing app I've found. It's possible to do some quite complex picture editing with a good range of tools, much more than most simple draw apps offer. Minimal permissions, most importantly no Internet permission and no ads. It would be great to have options when saving. Unfortunately it reduces the resolution and removes the EXIF data (most similar apps do the same), else it would be perfect.
replyContent: Thank you. Fixing these issues is planned for the future. Sorry, we are just pro-bono volunteers working in our free time on this free open source non-profit project... any help, e.g., as a developer would be highly appreciated. Thanks again for your kind understanding!

sentence: I 'm honestly surprised by this app .

That alone isn't special, however it does not have ads, in-app-purchases of any kind or even network access to grab your personal data. I expected I'd have to block network access. But I did not. Good app, worked fine for my purposes so far. Highly recommend. Would consider donating if the option was given.

sentence: Amazing paint/photo editing app !
content: Amazing paint/photo editing app! Ad free and has many excellent tools. Perfect alternative to Microsoft Paint. My main issue is the tools at the bottom are a little unorganized and a little tricky to navigate. Would be cool if it had a feature to organize the tools yourself. Also the resize tool can only shrink an image and not grow them. Please add this in a future update! Otherwise it's an outstanding app!
